Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the rhythm of the wind, deductions become clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Figuring out the alibi trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crime was caught on camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan's reasoning takes off the mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that one truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:48.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran and I accompanied Pops on the job to go see a pro wrestling match.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The main event of the day was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the title match between Jr. heavyweight champion Wolf Face and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,young ace, Hyota Nagase.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, just before the match...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nagase!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.71,0:02:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nagase was killed in the waiting room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coincidentally, the scene of the crime was videotaped
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:20.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wolf Face!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:30.83,Title,,0,0,0,,THE SULLIED MASKED HERO\N(Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:34.63,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Touto Sumo Stadium
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true that Nagase-senshu was injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When will the police make a statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, starting from the right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please tell us your name and where you were at approximately 7:20.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm Ushigome Iwao.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:54.32,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ushigome Iwao (36)\NPro Wrestler
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:56.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,At around 7:20, I was in the stands watching Kiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} gets mad if we don't watch his matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was there anyone watched it together with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I was by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, some of the guests may have remembered me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone was focused on Kiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s match, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was also watching Kiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s match by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:22.14,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sakuma Hiroyuki (25)\NPro Wrestler
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.51,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My name is Sakuma Hiroyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,But, after Kiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s match...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I immediately came to this room to call Nagase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nagase's match was right afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard this person's voice saying, "Nagase, hurry and come out"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that was after the time of the crime, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You in the wolf mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you could take your mask off and speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't understand Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Wolf-Face is Mexican.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, taking off his mask in front of a child and young girl is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind, Sakuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.51,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Oogami Takaharu (27)\NPro Wrestler
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.51,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Because those children already know who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, you're the good-looking, but super weak Oogami Takaharu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, isn't it even printed in this morning's Touto Sports...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A photograph of you and Wolf side-by-side!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuma here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He often stands in for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to confuse reporters and fans that stake out the gym and stadium trying to figure out Wolf-Face's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the mask you just removed and the mask in this photograph...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems they're somehow different...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a mealtime mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's made of a thin material, with fewer embellishments, and the mouth is made larger in order to make it easier to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:05:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I never thought Wolf-Face's identity could have been Oogami-senshu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Y-You, if I remember correctly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You disappeared from the public eye after your loss to Wolf-Face in "Mascara contra máscara"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.12,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Leonardo Rossi (30)\NPro Wrestler (Nega Wolf)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You're Leonardo Rossi, aren't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ma-Mascara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mascara contra máscara...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an unmasking match!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who loses has his mask removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought for sure that you'd retired...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leo had decided to retire after he lost to me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was stopped by Kiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Re-debuted in Japan wearing a Wolf-Face mask with the coloring changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, people started saying he looked like a shadowed wolf, and he became popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Nagase, it'd been decided that e'd be the next Junior Heavyweight challenger, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one expected something like this to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So where were you two at around 7:20?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it was right before the match, I was in the foreign wrestlers' locker room doing warm-up exercises by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because all of the other foreign wrestlers were out watching Kiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s match.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you were also watching Kiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s match?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short, all four of you have no alibis, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This crime could not have been committed if the culprit could not obtain Wolf-Face's mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus, the culprit is one who could come and go from the foreign wrestlers' locker room freely—one of those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wolf-Face's mask is packed into a bag along with the spare masks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hidden in the restroom that is off-limits to all but authorized personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that the mask can be put on in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for that, I'd be suspected of being Wolf-Face due to going in and out of the foreign wrestlers' locker room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I have already handed that bag over to the forensics officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only the victim had left some sort of dying message for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, I was saying earlier that a pro wrestling move was popular in our karate club?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name of that move is similar to "dying message".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that possibly be, "Diving Body Attack"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one Mil Mascaras does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe Bruiser Brody's Flying Knee Drop, or the Funks' Spinning Toe Hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was a Japanese wrestler's move...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, it's definitely Mutou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, anyhow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll investigate here some more, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please standby in a separate room with Takagi here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran, you too—take that brat and go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Detective Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:23.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a wrestler from a bloody bout.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Kayama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You almost look like a mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, this is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Nagase was stabbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Detective Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you about two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, about the masked...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that it's like that for everyone at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masks are generally like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, that includes Wolf-Face's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just forgot something in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I accidentally forgot something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, where did I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The report from forensics has come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:38.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bloodstains on the mask discovered in the restroom matched the victim's blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the hair, including from the eyebrows, inside the mask all matched those from the other Wolf-Face masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:10:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the mask was not worn by anyone other than the mask's original owner, Oogami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the victim's fingernails?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They checked thoroughly, but found nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he grabbed at the mask intending to rip it off, some of the culprit's skin should have remained on his fingernails.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit wasn't accustomed to being a wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:38.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an unshakable truth that inside the mask that the culprit wore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only Oogami-senshu's scalp and eyebrow hair were found.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this, it seems we can't but think of him as the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should also have known about the hidden camera set up by the TV station in this room where the crime took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:03.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he do something like wearing his own mask, knowing that it would bring suspicion upon himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might have been his intention to have us think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using reverse psychology, making us doubt that he would have done such a thing on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if we call Oogami-senshu in here again and ask him about it, I'm sure he'll confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he doesn't seem like such a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:25.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le-le!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something strange about this mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rear part of the mask the culprit is wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rear, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The design is different from the one Oogami-senshu was wearing earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:46.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The design?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, the mask from earlier had tufts of fur on the back as well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mask from this video doesn't have them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could this mask be a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may be a reproduction that they sell in the fan shops, or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is, perhaps, the mask from when Wolf-Face debuted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oogami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had said that even the retired masks were inside the same bag, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible that the culprit just happened to choose the old mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I thought I told you to keep watch over those four suspects!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} hadn't come back, so I was asked to come and take a look by Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that means that the design of the mask has absolutely nothing to do with this crime, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Iwas...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Ah-le-le" about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The irrelevant things you notice only serve to disrupt the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you set this room up in a manner I describe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you please bring the four suspects that are waiting in the separate room here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, let's strip it off, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sheep's clothing from the murderous wolf who stabbed Nagase{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to death in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey,look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those four people are going back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, a little while ago Mouri Kogorou also went into that room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogorou's Deduction Show?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm going to pass this chance up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us record it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's going to be a deduction show, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:13:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is still inside—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calling us back here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, you just said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I think we'll find out shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you four disguise yourselves as wolves as the culprit did and walk towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, Wolf-Face himself, Oogami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please put on the mask you're holding in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we have you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, come towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, now what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And next, Sakuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take the mask from Oogami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you tell the difference between the two of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us in! Let us in! Let us in! Let us in! Let us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, finally, Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wear this, and go over there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably have some sort of plan in mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:16:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't tell us where or what to take notice of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:01.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that all right, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd already predicted as much, but now it's perfectly clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who murdered Nagase{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}—you were the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the culprit in the video...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You kept glancing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glancing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll understand if you try the mask on, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The field of vision on wrestlers' masks is narrower than it appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're not used to wearing one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to fully grasp the situation before your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd unconsciously survey your surroundings, and trip over things in the blind spot at your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oogami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who is accustomed to wearing the Wolf-Face mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leonardo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who wears the Nega Wolf mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Sakuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who often stands in for Oogami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those three are excluded from being the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who is not accustomed to wearing that mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one remaining is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because I was glancing around and stumbled, you want to say I'm the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you want evidence, it's recorded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, in the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, where Conan pointed out earlier, on the back of the mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something extra...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mask strings...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are four of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit was wearing the thin mealtime mask stacked under thafmask!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, the culprit's hair wouldn't get on the inside of the blood-splattered mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, even though the victim tore the culprit's mask with his fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no trace of the culprit's skin on his fingernails.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't this be that mealtime mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier, when you fell down, it came out of your pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just something I was carrying in order to surprise some of the young people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not the mask the culprit was wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Butthat's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wolf-Face's mask is only black and white, but there are red splotches near the right eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the right eye of the mask you were wearing on top got ripped, the blood splatter got on here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well get the rest at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hat's right, I killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That fool who betrayed us, and was going to transfer to Worldwide Pro Wrestlers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to pin the crime on you, the unpopular young wrestler, and take the mask for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that I could become Wolf-Face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you hear a strange sound just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I just wear this mask, I can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't become Wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because even if you hide your face with a mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your soot-stained nature that treats pro wrestling with contempt cannot be concealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:19:59.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Youngster, what the hell do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shining Wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I was finally able to remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterward, the culprit Ushigome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} received a silent reprimand from Kiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And was taken from the white mat to the dim and gloomy prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.04,0:22:36.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it'll be difficult for you all from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be attacked endlessly by the media...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'll say things like "Pro Wrestling Murder Organization"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We wrestlers are tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're accustomed to being hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.68,0:22:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:22:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're a group of extremely tough men.
