Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, Oogami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, from the top rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oogami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you just talking about Wolf-Face?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.17,0:23:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, ookami!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ookami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, because ookami means wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wolf-Face's identity will... probably... never be revealed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.52,0:23:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably...
